            <title>[SOLR-2275] Spaces around mm parameter in dismax configuration cause NumberFormatException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2275</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Any whitespace around simple mm parameters in the configuration file produces a NumberFormatException at SolrPluginUtils.java:625. E.g. &amp;lt;str&amp;gt; 2 &amp;lt;str&amp;gt;. Adding whitespace in tests also causes this error to occur.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
