                            <comment id="12969612" author="erickerickson" created="Thu, 9 Dec 2010 02:34:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If someone wants to assign this to me (Erick Erickson), I&apos;ll fix it this weekend. And can someone see if there&apos;s a way that I can take JIRA issues for myself?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12969627" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Thu, 9 Dec 2010 05:06:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just added you as a &quot;contributor&quot; to JIRA... hopefully that should do the trick.  Can you try again?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12969715" author="erickerickson" created="Thu, 9 Dec 2010 12:35:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Yonik, that worked.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12970561" author="erickerickson" created="Sun, 12 Dec 2010 02:20:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve attached a patch for this issue. It may be a little bit of overkill, but it handles random whitespace in various expressions, I&apos;ve updated the tests by adding spaces around various expressions. For instance, &quot; 3 &amp;lt; -25% 10 &amp;lt; -3\n&quot;, &quot; \n-25%\n &quot;, &quot; \n3\n &quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let me know if there are changes you&apos;d like to see...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12970563" author="erickerickson" created="Sun, 12 Dec 2010 02:21:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s the patch, see previous comment.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
